<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>html19.png</title>
  <style>
    body{margin:0;height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#111827);font-family:Inter,system-ui,Arial;color:#e5e7eb}
    .wrap{width:740px;background:#0b1220;padding:48px;border-radius:20px;
      box-shadow:0 16px 44px rgba(0,0,0,.55);text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
    .glow{position:absolute;inset:-40%;background:radial-gradient(400px 220px at 20% 10%,rgba(56,189,248,.25),transparent 60%),
                                   radial-gradient(340px 200px at 90% 80%,rgba(244,114,182,.25),transparent 60%)}
    h1{margin:0 0 10px;font-size:34px;color:#38bdf8}
    p{margin:0 0 18px;color:#cbd5e1}
    .row{display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
    .tag{padding:8px 12px;border-radius:999px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);font-weight:700;font-size:13px}
    .badge{position:absolute;top:16px;left:16px;background:#38bdf8;color:#0f172a;font-weight:800;padding:6px 10px;border-radius:10px;font-size:12px}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="badge">Version 19</div>
    <h1>RGZTEC Demo 19</h1>
    <p>Placeholder to export as <strong>html19.png</strong>. Clean, modern, code-market vibe.</p>
    <div class="row">
      <span class="tag">components</span><span class="tag">widgets</span><span class="tag">templates</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
